      "retrievedDate": "2026-07-02",
      "quotedText": "Clark County Community Fishing Ponds: Boulder City Pond, Sunset Park Pond, Floyd Lamb Park Ponds, Lorenzi Park Pond and Mesquite Urban Pond \u2013 Hafen Lane Pond. Open year around. Daily: 3 game fish. Possession: 6 game fish. Hours parks are open to public use."
